 {r}‚ÜêHandleLinkSourceFlags path;linkcfgFile;linkconfig;nameList;opCode;q;deleteFlag
‚çù Stops and traces are potentially stored in a file .link.config
‚çù If such a file exists and carries SourceFlags *and* the global Cider setting `HandleLinkStops` is greater
‚çù than 0 then this function takes action://
‚çù * HandleLinkStops=1 the user is asked whether she wants to erase stop and trace settings from `.linkconfig`
‚çù * HandleLinkStops=2 stop and trace settings are erase from `.linkconfig` without asking\\
‚çù The file will be deleted if it does not contain anything but the Link version the file was written with.
‚çù `path` must be the source folder of a project; that's where Link stores the `.linkconfig` file.
‚çù Returns 0 for "na action taken", 1 for "file was deleted" and 2 for "file was changed".
 r‚Üê0
 linkcfgFile‚Üêpath,'/.linkconfig'
 :If F.IsFile linkcfgFile
     linkconfig‚ÜêGet_JSON5 linkcfgFile
     nameList‚Üê(linkconfig.‚éïNL-2 9)~‚äÇ'LinkVersion'
 :AndIf (‚äÇ'SourceFlags')‚àänameList
     opCode‚ÜêGetGlobalHandleLinkStops
 :AndIf 0<opCode
     deleteFlag‚Üê0
     :If 2=opCode
         linkconfig.‚éïEX'SourceFlags'
         deleteFlag‚Üê1
     :ElseIf 0=‚â¢nameList~‚äÇ'SourceFlags'
         q‚Üê'StopsAndTraces@There are ',‚äÉ{‚ç∫,' and ',‚çµ}/(0<‚äÉ¬®linkconfig.SourceFlags.‚éïNC'Stop' 'Trace')/'stops' 'traces'
         q,‚Üê' saved in .linkconfig',(‚éïUCS 13),'Would you like to delete those?'
         :If 1 CommTools.YesOrNo q
             linkconfig.‚éïEX'SourceFlags'
             deleteFlag‚Üê1
         :EndIf
     :EndIf
     :If deleteFlag
     :AndIf 0=‚â¢nameList~‚äÇ'SourceFlags'
         F.DeleteFile linkcfgFile           ‚çù There was nothing else in it, se we delete it
         r‚Üê1
     :Else
         linkconfig Put_JSON5 linkcfgFile   ‚çù There is other stuff as well, so we write it back
         r‚Üê2
     :EndIf
 :EndIf
